So now that you have
two of the books

00:12:33.980 --> 00:12:37.810
out, anything that you would
have changed in book one or two

00:12:37.810 --> 00:12:39.869
or maybe done a
little differently?

00:12:39.869 --> 00:12:41.160
PAT ROTHFUSS: Who's the author?

00:12:41.160 --> 00:12:46.210
Oh, right, I know that,
let's not go there.

