starting to develop fine motor

01:02:09.340 --> 01:02:14.230
coordination, and little
sweaty kid fingers,

01:02:14.230 --> 01:02:17.970
ladies you have no-- whoa--
you have no idea how much it

01:02:17.970 --> 01:02:20.710
hurts to have your beard pulled.

01:02:20.710 --> 01:02:25.070
It's right on one of the most
sensitive parts of your body,

01:02:25.070 --> 01:02:28.130
you get a little kid with
his sweaty fingers in there,

01:02:28.130 --> 01:02:33.370
and then he just pulls on it,
and you cannot cuss him out.

01:02:33.370 --> 01:02:36.380
You have to say,
ah, daddy loves you,

01:02:36.380 --> 01:02:41.000
he's crying so much
